// Theme palette — Stylus VARIABLES ONLY.
//
// VuePress injects this file into every component's <style> block (so SFCs can
// read $accentColor, layout vars, etc.). It must therefore NOT emit any CSS
// rules: an emitted selector here is duplicated into every SFC and produces
// scoped [data-v-*] copies, bloating the bundle. All selectors that actually
// paint the modes/themes live in styles/index.styl (compiled once, globally).

